Dia tampak menawan di layar.

45
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,780
Cantik sekali!

46
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:03,660
Jangan terlalu gembira.

47
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:05,870
Masyarakat sudah menggila,

48
00:04:05,950 --> 00:04:07,710
kata mereka, korban yang malang

49
00:04:07,790 --> 00:04:09,370
harus mengajukan banding.

50
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,630
Ini gawat.

51
00:04:11,710 --> 00:04:14,210
Opini publik itu emosional,
tapi hukum itu logis.

52
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:17,340
Benar, kan? Kita berbicara melalui hasil.

53
00:04:17,420 --> 00:04:20,260
Jika hasilnya tak bersalah,
itulah jawabannya.

54
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:23,890
- Baiklah.
- Aku Jaksa Kim Gi-wook…

55
00:04:24,970 --> 00:04:26,640
Jaksanya tampak malang.

56
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,310
Dia pasti akan dimarahi.

57
