Mereka mengadakan rapat darurat
di Kantor Distrik Pusat Seoul.

62
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,700
Omong-omong, bagaimana dia menang?

63
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:44,660
Ada rekaman CCTV dan saksi mata.

64
00:04:44,740 --> 00:04:47,200
Itu sebabnya dia jadi rekanan semuda itu.

65
00:04:47,290 --> 00:04:49,250
PENGACARA MAENG SE-NA
SELAMAT JADI REKANAN

66
00:04:49,330 --> 00:04:52,750
