72
00:05:05,350 --> 00:05:07,770
Lebih seperti AI atau android.

73
00:05:07,850 --> 00:05:09,100
Tak punya emosi,

74
00:05:09,730 --> 00:05:14,020
tak punya pacar, keluarga, teman.
Dia selalu bekerja.

75
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:18,570
Kecuali dia robot,
tak mungkin manusia bisa hidup begitu.

76
00:05:19,690 --> 00:05:21,490
Teorimu sangat menarik.

77
00:05:25,370 --> 00:05:27,200
Hari ini, jaksa kasusnya mengatakan…

78
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:29,580
Pengacara Maeng!

79
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,160
Kapan kau datang?

80
