134
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:04,350
Apa ini?

135
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,560
Dia bagai patung.

136
00:10:12,490 --> 00:10:13,320
Kabari aku

137
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:16,200
tentang pemotretan Do Ra-ik

138
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:18,660
seperti alarm darurat.

139
00:10:23,290 --> 00:10:27,290
"It's Me" dari Do Ra-ik sukses besar.

